OL,3,CProject Vigilant scheme aims to make
OL,4,Cnights out safer
OL,6,FA scheme aimed at tackling predatory
OL,7,Fbehaviours like harassment, loitering
OL,8,Fwithout reason and stalking has been
OL,9,Flaunched by the PSNI.
OL,11,FProject Vigilant is being piloted in
OL,12,FLondonderry and will see increased
OL,13,Fpatrols in the city at night, as both
OL,14,Funiformed and plain clothed officers
OL,15,Fwill target pubs and clubs in a bid to
OL,16,Fmake women feel safe.
OL,18,FIn the year up to 31 July, there were
OL,19,Fover 2,000 rape and sexual assault
OL,20,Foffences reported to police.
