OL,3,CProject Vigilant scheme aims to make
OL,4,Cnights out safer
OL,6,F"The operations will be carried out
OL,7,Fwith the aim of proactively preventing
OL,8,Fviolence and sexual offences against
OL,9,Fwomen and girls, whilst also ensuring
OL,10,Fanyone of any gender can enjoy their
OL,11,Fnight out safely," a spokesperson said.
OL,13,F"On Halloween night alone plain
OL,14,Fclothed and uniformed officers working
OL,15,Ftogether made an arrest for upskirting
OL,16,Fand intervened in six situations where
OL,17,Fpredatory behaviours were being
OL,18,Fdisplayed towards vulnerable people,
OL,19,Fincluding towards a child from a
OL,20,Fchildren's home.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
