OL,3,CProject Vigilant scheme aims to make
OL,4,Cnights out safer
OL,6,F"Alongside this new activity, the
OL,7,FPolice Service has also introduced a
OL,8,Fnew internal mapping tool, where all
OL,9,Freports of violence, abuse or
OL,10,Fintimidation of women and girls feed
OL,11,Finto.
OL,13,F"This allows local officers to
OL,14,Fidentify the 'problem' areas and
OL,15,Ftarget resources to these spaces."
