OL,3,CProject Vigilant scheme aims to make
OL,4,Cnights out safer
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Gillian Kearney,
OL,7,FDistrict Commander for Derry/
OL,8,FLondonderry and PSNI Lead for Project
OL,9,FVigilant said a lot of people,
OL,10,Fparticularly women and girls, are "not
OL,11,Ffeeling safe when out at night".
OL,13,F"We're pleased to be launching an
OL,14,Finitial pilot of this initiative
OL,15,Facross Northern Ireland as part of our
OL,16,Fcontinued commitment to address
OL,17,Ftargeted predatory behaviours,
OL,18,Fparticularly towards women and girls,"
OL,19,Fshe said.
