OL,3,CProject Vigilant scheme aims to make
OL,4,Cnights out safer
OL,6,F"We know that the hospitality sector
OL,7,Fin Derry/Londonderry works hard to
OL,8,Fcreate safe places for people to go
OL,9,Fout and have fun so this is another
OL,10,Fway that we are working in partnership
OL,11,Fto make their customers feel even
OL,12,Fsafer.
OL,14,F"We will have eyes and ears in night
OL,15,Ftime economy spaces, and not always in
OL,16,Funiform, looking out for anybody who
OL,17,Fis showing signs of potential
OL,18,Fperpetrator behaviours and intervening
OL,19,Fbefore they might go on to commit a
OL,20,Fserious sexual offence.
