OL,3,CProject Vigilant scheme aims to make
OL,4,Cnights out safer
OL,6,F"I recognise that people have the
OL,7,Fright to go out and enjoy their night
OL,8,Fwithout feeling like the police are
OL,9,Fwatching them, but it is crucial we
OL,10,Fare operating in this way, in these
OL,11,Fspaces ` it is the right thing to do.
OL,13,F"Instead of just putting out personal
OL,14,Fsafety advice, we are telling the
OL,15,Fpublic that we are proactively
OL,16,Ftargeting those who may jeopardise
OL,17,Ftheir safety and making them safer as
OL,18,Fa result."
